rows.label: qst102107_msg0002
rows.name:
I wish I had better news, but...
things have gotten worse.

rows.label: qst102107_msg0003
rows.name:
Someone took advantage of the
chaos to raid the armory.

rows.label: qst102107_msg0004
rows.name:
The timing is too perfect...
There's a high probability
our spy is involved.

rows.label: qst102107_msg0005
rows.name:
Please, find the culprit
and the weapons.

rows.label: qst102107_msg0006
rows.name:
I've tightened security at the
entrances so no one can get out.

rows.label: qst102107_msg0007
rows.name:
They must still be
somewhere in the village.
